<style>
    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        font-weight:200;
        padding:30px;
    }

    form {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 3px solid #3498db;
        border-radius: 15px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .form-label {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #555;
    }

    .form-control {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        border: 2px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: border-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #3498db;
        }

    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #217dbb;
        }

    .data {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: auto;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

        .data h3 {
            color: #3498db;
        }

        .data p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Optional: Add some styling for a button or input fields if needed */
        .data button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .data input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

    div.full {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        margin:40px;
    }


</style>

<div class="full">

    <div class="data">
        <h3>EDUREGIST</h3>
        <P>
            Welcome to EduRegist, where seamless access meets educational excellence! Unlock the gateway to a world
            of learning with our user-friendly login portal. Your journey begins here, where innovation meets
            convenience, ensuring a hassle-free experience as you embark on your educational adventure. Dive into a
            realm of possibilities and knowledge with just a click. Join EduRegist today, where logging in is the
            first step towards unlocking the doors to a brighter future. Let the journey commence!
        </P>
    </div>
    <form method="post">
        <h1>Register for mew account</h1>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">Username</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="Username">
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">Email</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="Email">
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">Password</label>
            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="Password">
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </form>
</div>

